source_material_quote:
- (i) As part of  the  mitigation measures  against fraud and  corruption and  to  ensure maximum transparency and accountability over  the  use  of  Project's funds; during  the procurement and implementation period the  following will  be  monitored: (a) Bid  evaluation periods;

- (b) Number of  responses to  bid  invitations; (c)  Contract management,  including number

- of  variation orders; (c)  Comparison of lowest responsive bids against cost estimates; and (d) Nature  and  frequency of  complaints.

